data.description: PEACEFUL SECLUSION describes this 1997 well insulated site built home w/attached double garage (25X20) & front covered patio. This 3BR/2BA/1456SF+/- home is on a 2 acre level parcel,fenced & all useable! Eat in kitchen w/breakfast bar & built in microwave, dining nook, wood burning stove in living room; walk in closet in MBR & dual vanity in MBA. Landscaped yard w/mature shade trees/variety of fruit trees & all on a drip irrigation system; RV hook up; ample space to park RV,boat,ATV's! NO restrictions! Horses welcomed! Mtn. views! Close to beautiful Lake Roosevelt & easy access to Forest Service roads for ATV riding, hunting, hiking!  Harvesting and cultivating is allowed.
data.whatILove: Peaceful! Plenty room for parking boat trailer r.v what ever you have. Lots of mature fruit trees, plenty of room for gardening and horses. Close to National Forest and Roosevelt Lake for recreation.
